snippet.textDisplay:
What a masterpiece ❤️
The focus on guitar and the percussions at 01:59 and later, on Khartal, at 04:10 is just incredible. The entire composition is so beautiful. I hardly understand a word but the song and its music is extremely addictive. The beautiful ensemble of the Sarangi with every other instrument used in this composition along with the vocals by the great Mame Khan is perfect! Love from the South (Bengaluru) :)
